  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<section class=\"webinar-detail\">\n<div class=\"webinar-hero-banner hero__container hero__container--text-dark hero__container--no-overlay hero__container--color\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<h1 class=\"webinar-title\">\n<span>Closing the Gap: Parametric Insurance for a Volatile World</span>\n</h1>\n<span data-item-id=\"80655\" data-price=\"49.00\" data-product=\"Closing the Gap: Parametric Insurance for a Volatile World\" data-react-component-id=\"add-to-cart\">\n<button class=\"btn btn--primary btn--disabled\">Add to Cart -\t\t\t\t\t\t&amp;dollar;49.00</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width container__flex u-padding-top\">\n<span class=\"u-text-uppercase badge badge--dark badge--icon\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-calendar-dims\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#calendar\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div><time datetime=\"2026-02-05T16:00:00Z\">Feb. 05 2026 11:00 AM EST</time>\n</div>\n</span>\n<div class=\"webinar-block u-margin-bottom\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"webinar-description u-padding-bottom\">\n<p>Gain a clear understanding of parametric insurance: how index triggers are defined, verified, and paid; how it complements indemnity policies; and how to communicate basis risk. Examine market drivers, policy anatomy, and regulatory considerations. Explore real applications including NYC pilots, ag, microinsurance, travel delay, cyber outages, and renewable energy. Understand the role of satellites, sensors, and third-party data, practical payout formulas, and strategies to reduce mismatch risk, with examples across municipalities, SMEs, and global programs. </p><ul><li><span>Standard Webinar Price: $49.00</span></li><li><span>CEU Unlimited Subscriber Price: Included in your subscription.</span><ul><li><em>*CEU Unlimited subscriber webinar discount will be reflected in the checkout process. <span style=\"color:#A31E2C;\"><strong>No 